title: Animal sound ringtones free
description:
Assign an animal sound to each of your contacts. When you are called, you may know by the sound who is the contact that is calling you. Educational application for children and adults, contains sounds, images and videos of a wide variety of animals.
Ideal to teach and learn about the animal kingdom, illustrate with images, reproduce sounds of animals and show videos of documentaries about their interaction with the environment that surrounds them.
You have the option to add the sounds as a cell phone tone.
Enjoy it, we hope your suggestions to improve this application.
